    </div>
    <div class="col s9 trainingPlanDisplay">
      <div class="card-panel grey lighten-2">
        <h4 class="center planName">"A goal without a plan is just a wish."</h4>
        <div id="showThePlan">
          <p>Whether you are training for a 5k or a marathon it is essential to have a plan or you will quickly find yourself off track.  Choose a plan here and use it to keep yourself on track for a successful race day.</p>

          <p><a href="http://halhigdon.com/" target="_blank">Hal Higdon</a> is a renowned running coach and long time contributor to Runner's World Magazine.  The training plans provided here are courtesy of Hal Higdon and are some of the most utilized and successful plans available today.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
